===Noun===
'''sustain'''
#{{music}} A [[mechanism]] which can be used to [[hold]] a note, as the left [[pedal]] on a [[piano]].

===Transitive verb===
'''to sustain'''
#To [[maintain]] something, or keep it in [[existence]]
#To [[provide for]] something, or [[nourish]] it
#To [[encourage]] something
#To [[experience]] or [[suffer]] an [[injury]] etc
#To [[confirm]], [[prove]] or [[corroborate]] something
